-- Canada BHP ruling to come after 4:30 EDT Wednesday
-- 
-- Wed Nov 3, 2010 9:00am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/11/03/us-potashcorp-canada-timing-idUSTRE6A23T320101103

 

 OTTAWA  (Reuters) - Canada's decision on whether it plans to allow or block a bid by BHP Billiton for Potash Corp will be released after 4:30 pm (2030 GMT) on Wednesday, an official said. 

 The deadline for a decision is midnight on Wednesday (0400 GMT Thursday). (Reporting by  David Ljunggren )